          "x": 36,
          "y": 36,
          "width": 108,
          "height": 108,
          "title": "Murder Atlas: New Orleans Edition",
          "tagline": "Follow a trail of scandal and mystery through the city's shadowy past.",
          "guideName": "David Hennessy",
          "price": "Free To Start / In App Purchases",
          "tags": [
            "TRUE CRIME",
            "Horror",
            "New Orleans"
          ],
          "body": "Every major city in the world has its share of death. New Orleans just made an art form of it. In Murder Atlas: New Orleans Edition, you’ll follow a trail of scandal, mystery, and blood through the city’s shadowy past, where jazz music can literally save your life.\n\nTrack clues, interrogate suspects, and outrun the shadows in a city of jazz, ghosts, and unsolved horrors, where the legend of the Axeman still hangs in the air.\n\nYou must be in New Orleans to start the game.\n\nIf you’re already here, text JAZZ to begin.",
          "varName": "",
          "anytime": false,
          "anytimePairId": "",
          "rotation": 0
        }
